## Women's College Basketball Rankings Shake-Up: Louisville Soars to No. 6
The latest women's college basketball rankings have been released, and there's been a significant shake-up in the top 10. The Louisville Cardinals have surged to No. 6, thanks to their impressive performance on the court. This comes just ahead of their highly anticipated ACC clash with the Duke Blue Devils. On the other hand, the Maryland Terrapins have taken a tumble in the rankings.
